What is React ? 
1. js library to build Dynamic and interactive user interface 
2. develop facebook in 2011
3. currently most widely used js libary for fornt-end development 
4. used to create single page application  . (spa)


working of DOM
1. Browser takes HTML and create DOM
2. js helps us modify DOM based on user actions or events
3. in big application, Working with dom becomes complicated 


Problem with javascript 
1. React has a simpler mental model
2. js is cumbersome
3. Js is error-prone 
4. js is hard to maintaine 


working of react 
1. No need to worry about querying and updating dom 
2. react creates a web page with small and reusable 
3. React will take care of creating and updating DOM 
4. it saves a lot of time 


js vs react 

1. JS is imperative: You define steps to reach you desire state 
2. React is Delarative: you define the target ui state and then react figures how to reach that state


Introduction to Components 
1. react application is a tree of components with app component as the root bringing everything together 